column2: SELECT   t.ra, t.dec,t.plate,t.mjd,t.fiberid,    t.petromag_u, t.petromag_g, t.petromag_r, t.petromag_i, t.petromag_z,    g.oiii_#_eqw, g.h_alpha_eqw, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, t.z, t.objid as objid, t.specobjid as specobjid       into mydb.clu_objects8 FROM MyDB.clu AS m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.sdss_ra, m.sdss_dec, #) AS n    JOIN specphotoall AS t ON n.objid=t.objid   JOIN galspecline AS g ON t.specobjid=g.specobjid
